data.title: Spring of 2023 Dean’s List
data.meta_description: Earning a spot on the Clemson University Dean's List is a remarkable achievement. Here is a list of students on the Spring 2023 Dean's List.
data.text:
Paula Powers

Share:

Earning a spot on the Clemson University Dean’s List is a remarkable achievement. This prestigious honor is granted to students who achieve a minimum 3.5-grade point average while completing at least 12 semester hours, excluding Pass/No Pass coursework.

Below is a comprehensive listing of the Spring 2023 Dean’s List, sorted alphabetically, according to last names.

To celebrate this significant milestone, visit the University’s President’s and Dean’s List website. There, create a personalized badge by entering a student’s name and downloading the image to save, send or share.
